            Your entire HR.<br>One system.
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-3 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-[#555555]">
            From hiring to payroll — Limendo mERP powered by Frappe HR handles
            every part of your workforce in one place.
          </p>

          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            {benefits.map((item) => (
              <li class="flex gap-2 items-center text-sm text-[#333333]">
                <div class="check-dot h-4 w-4 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
